Cahier des Charges: Aminoss Photography Portfolio
1️⃣ Project Overview

Project Name: Aminoss Photography Portfolio
Objective: Create a professional, visually striking photography portfolio that:

Displays all photography and video works

Has an Instagram-style grid layout

Includes professional features: categories, lightbox, video reels, About & Contact pages

Allows easy media uploading and management via Cloudinary

Does not require any client login

Target Audience:

Potential clients (weddings, portraits, fashion, travel)

Art enthusiasts and followers

Agencies seeking professional photographers

2️⃣ Functional Requirements
2.1 Home Page

Hero section with featured photo or video

Instagram-style photo grid showcasing latest works

Categories filter: Weddings, Portrait, Travel, Fashion, Videos

Smooth hover effects and animations

Lightbox popup for full image/video view

2.2 Gallery Page

Full grid layout with infinite scroll

Filters by category

Lightbox view with:

Image/video full display

Description of the work

Camera & lens info (optional)

Location/project info

2.3 Videos / Reels Page

Embedded videos (Cloudinary, YouTube, Vimeo)

Fullscreen playback

Categories or playlist organization

2.4 About Page

Photographer biography and philosophy

Awards, exhibitions, collaborations

Option to download PDF portfolio

2.5 Contact Page

Contact form (name, email, message)

Social media links (Instagram, Facebook, YouTube)

Optional booking information

2.6 Admin / CMS

No client login required

Only the photographer can manage content

Admin functions:

Add, edit, remove images/videos

Manage categories and featured projects

Upload media directly to Cloudinary

3️⃣ Non-Functional Requirements
3.1 Performance

Fast loading times

Fully responsive design (desktop, tablet, mobile)

Optimized images via Cloudinary (resizing, compression)

3.2 Security

HTTPS / SSL support (via Vercel)

Sanitized contact form inputs

3.3 Scalability

Can host thousands of photos/videos

Easy to add new categories or collections

3.4 SEO & Marketing

SEO-friendly URLs, meta tags, structured data

Social sharing tags (Open Graph for Facebook, Twitter cards)

Optional analytics integration (Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel)

4️⃣ Technical Specifications
Component	Technology / Tool
Frontend	Next.js + TailwindCSS
Hosting	Vercel (free plan)
Images / Video Storage	Cloudinary (free plan)
Backend / API	Optional Node.js + Express (only if a CMS is needed)
Database	Optional (not required if using Cloudinary)
5️⃣ Design Guidelines

Layout: Instagram-style grid

Theme: Modern, minimal, elegant

Colors: Neutral background (white/black) + accent colors for branding

Typography: Clean, professional fonts

Animations: Hover zoom, fade-in images, smooth lightbox transitions

UX: Easy navigation, interactive image and video browsing

6️⃣ Deployment & Maintenance

Frontend: Vercel (free)

Media Storage: Cloudinary

Maintenance: Upload new photos/videos via Cloudinary or optional CMS

No authentication required for visitors

7️⃣ Project Timeline (Estimated)
Phase	Duration	Tasks
Design	1 week	Wireframes, UI/UX mockups, colors, typography
Development	2-3 weeks	Frontend, grid layout, lightbox, pages
Integration	1 week	Cloudinary integration, optional CMS
Testing	1 week	Responsiveness, speed, SEO, functionality
Deployment	2 days	Hosting on Vercel, domain setup
8️⃣ Deliverables

Fully functional portfolio website

Home, Gallery, Videos, About, Contact pages

Instagram-style grid design with lightbox

Fully responsive, fast, SEO-friendly

Cloudinary integration for all media

Optional CMS for content management